text: Md. Habibur Rahman is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Satkhira-2. ==Career== Rahman was elected to parliament from Satkhira-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Md. Habibur Rahman
